245
00:13:20,880 --> 00:13:25,070
I found a great recipe for making chocolate
chip cookies.

246
00:13:25,070 --> 00:13:26,650
A recipe.

247
00:13:26,650 --> 00:13:30,610
But that's second word, receipt.

248
00:13:30,610 --> 00:13:33,280
So many letters that are cut out.

249
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:41,990
Receipt, re-, it sounds like R-U, receipt,
seat.

250
00:13:41,990 --> 00:13:50,890
So the P is cut out and the E-I is just an
